  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "This PS game brings the Bratz characters together in an adventure designed for girls of all ages. Unlike more traditional dolls such as Barbie, Bratz features a style inspired by Japanese anime and hip-hop fashion. The characters also come from a variety of ethnic backgrounds, which has helped fuel the popularity of the franchise.\n\nDress up to get down and be a Bratz superstar!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "All your favorite Bratz: Cloe, Yasmin, Sasha, Jade, and Meygan Dress up and then hit the dance floor in Dance Dance Revolution-style gameplay Earn new songs, clothes, stages, and dance steps through excellent play.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
